properties.name: Craftsman's center
properties.desc: You can just look around and also if you want to buy Craftsman's hand-made traditional clothes, carpet, paintings, etc.

properties.name: Marmar Bazaar
properties.desc: Small Bazaar located in the center of the city.  Even though the bazaar's name is written as "Marmar" at the enterance,  every people calls it "Kritirinka". It's not a big market. But you can buy almost all groceries including Non(Uzbek Staple dish). Additionally there are two mid-size supermarkets.

properties.name: Registon Supermarket
properties.desc: Western style big supermarket. You can buy almost all what you want but the price is expensive in the price level of this city.
